The rep for Waxoyl met in Europe told me that the best way to apply their 
product is to spay it on under pressure.  Waxoyl offers it in the UK at can 
with a pump sprayer.  The rep said this isn't effective to get the product 
into all the small places and seams where it need to go.   He gave me this 
link and number 781-662-1117 www.britishsportscars.com

